{"tid":2042052,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"黨軍：兩名猝死黨員沒參與反修例相關工作；另一名黨員疑中風送院 其後回復知覺","createTime":"2020-05-29T15:22:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-29T17:37:01.000Z","uid":21470,"like":31,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"91ab9056b21bb88dc231cabcc4285b1c5078a5a1","tid":2042052,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T15:22:06.000Z","msg":"警方對近日兩名警員猝逝感難過痛心<br />\n29.05.2020 23:12<br />\n<br />\n兩名警員分別昨日及今日在住所昏送，送院後證實不治。警方表示，確認近日有兩名休班警務人員離世，為此感到非常難過和痛心，已向相關人員的家人表示慰問，警隊福利服務課將會提供一切適切協助。警方指，事發前兩名警員負責警區正常軍裝職務，沒有參與反修例運動的執法工作，並如常休班，身故原因有待查證。<br />\n<br />\n駐守田心警署的56歲高級警員，昨晨在沙角邨寓所內昏迷，送院搶救後不治；另一名40歲警員是青衣警區特遣隊成員，下午約1時在荔景紀律部隊宿舍的洗手間內昏迷暈倒，家人報案送院搶救無效。另外，一名54歲交通警，下午約5時在紅磡西九龍交通行動基地當值期間不適，半清醒下被送往伊利沙伯醫院治理，其後回復知覺。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1293830&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1293830%26csid%3D261_341&d=MUobR5x4uSQxHz8Khhk%2FvAEDdXZq%2B7ycbDpBQOFx8Mg%3D&h=57fdf228\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1293830&amp;csid=261_341</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n54歲男警當值期間不適送院<br />\n29.05.2020 22:54<br />\n<br />\n一名54歲交通警，下午約5時在紅磡西九龍交通行動基地當值期間不適，半清醒下被送往伊利沙伯醫院治理，其後回復知覺，警方將事件列作警務人員當值期間不適。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1293812&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1293812%26csid%3D261_341&d=MUobR5x4uSQxHz8Khhk%2FvAEDdXZq%2B7ycbDpBQOFx8Mg%3D&h=41dde131\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1293812&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"376da059784a6dfa3fcec49a61b35fdb3ef4584b","tid":2042052,"uid":36383,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T15:24:07.000Z","msg":"白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />警"},{"pid":"ea71b75d8022ca52522ac255d0f8d1951dfa67c2","tid":2042052,"uid":118247,"like":31,"dislike":1,"score":30,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T15:28:52.000Z","msg":"正呀<br />\n一日三單<br />\n係咪有手足執到死亡筆記"},{"pid":"0c0a8b2f0ff4ce587c434727b7e3215a9dafe931","tid":2042052,"uid":113183,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T15:29:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">警方指，事發前兩名警員負責警區正常軍裝職務，沒有參與反修例運動的執法工作，並如常休班，身故原因有待查證。</span><br />\n<br />\n做咩此地無銀三百兩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20975e1a59d2a5ea93d55caba14e7ea1b4cc33f7","tid":2042052,"uid":74182,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T15:29:57.000Z","msg":"竟然回復知覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n請救救呢間黃店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8izXzT4C_fw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D8izXzT4C_fw&d=MUobR5x4uSQxHz8Khhk%2FvAEDdXZq%2B7ycbDpBQOFx8Mg%3D&h=64c39494\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8izXzT4C_fw</a>"},{"pid":"15ba478a50ba702209aa51a2c9d60e860cffb0a5","tid":2042052,"uid":264988,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T15:30:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mwj0tjD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fmwj0tjD.png&h=a5b414d2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"450a7ff1cd0604a3006b922e5c459b6a0e28862b","tid":2042052,"uid":122275,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T15:30:52.000Z","msg":"中共要清condom了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0189fb569df1a6661e309cecf985278338b292e","tid":2042052,"uid